### Fraud Detection — FraudDetectionAgent
### POST /api/fraud/detect
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### Low-risk transaction: small domestic purchase → auto APPROVE path
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/fraud/detect
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "transactionId": "TXN-10001",
  "accountId": "ACC-55220",
  "amount": 34.99,
  "merchantName": "Migros",
  "merchantCategory": "Grocery",
  "location": "Zurich, Switzerland",
  "timestamp": "2026-05-10T09:15:00Z"
}

###

